Package com.arjuna.ArjunaCore.Implementation

Class Summary
Implementations Module specific class that is responsible for adding any implementations to the inventory.
LockStoreImple Implementations of lock stores should derive from this abstract class and provide implementations of the appropriate methods.
ObjectStoreImple This is the base class from which all object store types are derived.
SemaphoreImple Implementations of semaphore classes should derive from this class and provide implementations of the relevant methods.
